refentry:
elements constraintdef constraintdef Element
constraintdef &constraintdef.purpose;
&constraintdef.synopsis.gen; Description
This element is only available if you are using the EBNF Module.
A ConstraintDef contains a description of a constraint that cannot be expressed in the grammar (generally logical rather than syntactic constraints).
Processing expectations
&format.block;
&constraintdef.parents.gen; &constraintdef.children.gen;
Examples
For examples, see &constraintdef.example.seealso.gen;.
